eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A REQUIRED WEEKLY TEST FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Yakima, WA; AT 03:03 PM ON OCT 31, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 06:03 PM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: This is the Required Weekly Test (RWT) of the local emergency alert system for Yakima County Washington. In the event of an emergency, broadcast stations would provide important public safety information. This is only a test.
